## PM Quiz — 5 Questions

**File:** `PMOnboardingQuiz.tsx`

| Q# | Question | Answer type | Options |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | What type of data feature are you building? | `featureType` | dashboard, table, chart, metrics, recommendations, filters, detail, form, other |
| 2 | How much data will this feature display? | `dataVolume` | small, medium, large, unknown, other |
| 3 | Do you have a PRD or requirements document? | `hasPRD` | yes, rough, no, other |
| 4 | Do you have a design reference? | `designRef` | figma, screenshot, none, other |
| 5 | How would you describe your experience level? | `experience` | new, familiar, advanced, other |

**Key difference from Designer quiz:** Q3 (`hasPRD`) answer is passed upstream via `onComplete`. The parent page uses it to show/hide the PRD Template section.

**"Other" answer handling:** When a user selects "Other", show an inline `TextField` below the radio options with a "Please describe" label. Save the text to `otherTexts[questionId]` and merge into `answers.otherText` on Next.

**Reading path logic (based on `featureType`):**

| featureType | Suggested pages |
|---|---|
| `dashboard` | Card, DataTable |
| `table` | DataTable |
| `chart` | Overview |
| `metrics` | Card |
| `recommendations` | Card, Button |
| `filters` | Select |
| `detail` | DataTable |
| `form` | Button |

