## 5. Conditional Content — PRD Template (PM only)

Show only when `hasPRD === 'no'` or `hasPRD === 'rough'`.

**PRD Template fields (9 text fields + 1 textarea):**

| Field ID | Label | Placeholder hint |
|---|---|---|
| `name` | Feature name | e.g. Campaign Performance Dashboard |
| `story` | User story | As a ___, I want to ___, so that ___ |
| `show` | What to display | e.g. Table of campaigns, KPI cards |
| `fields` | Data fields | e.g. Campaign name, daily budget, ROAS, status |
| `actions` | Actions | e.g. Sort, filter by status, export CSV |
| `filters` | Filters | e.g. Date range, campaign type |
| `volume` | Data volume | e.g. Up to 500 rows, paginated 20 per page |
| `empty` | Empty state | e.g. "No campaigns found" with CTA button |
| `outofscope` | Out of scope | e.g. No export, no inline editing |
| `notes` | Additional Notes (TextArea) | Any edge cases, constraints |

All fields use LD `TextField size="small"`. Notes uses `TextArea size="small"`.
Show a progress bar (`filled / total * 100%`) and a **"Copy PRD as prompt"** button.

