## 7. How It Works (PM)

4 numbered steps with circle badges and descriptions:

```
1. You describe the feature       — quiz, PRD, or plain language
2. The agent analyzes requirements — maps to LD components, flags rule conflicts
3. The agent builds the feature   — production-ready code, tokens, a11y
4. You review and iterate         — changes appear in live preview
```

