## 8. Data Feature Patterns (PM)

6 cards in a responsive grid (`minmax(280px, 1fr)`):

| Pattern | Description |
|---|---|
| Performance Dashboard | Metric cards + chart + data table. Campaign overviews. |
| Data Table with Filters | Filterable, sortable, resizable. Keyword/item reports. |
| KPI Card Grid | Responsive grid with trend indicators. Executive summaries. |
| Recommendation Cards | Carousel or list with Apply/Dismiss actions. |
| Chart + Summary | Chart with legend, time controls, stats. Trend analysis. |
| Detail Panel | Resizable side panel from row/card click. Drill-down views. |

