## 9. Quick-Start Prompts (Both pages)

A collapsible `<Accordion>` inside a `CollapsibleSection` wrapper.
Each category is an `AccordionItem` with 3–6 prompt chips inside.

**Prompt chip behavior:**
- Click chip → copies full prompt to clipboard
- Chevron icon → toggles expanded view of the full prompt text
- Copied state → chip turns green with ✓ for 1.5 seconds

**Designer prompt categories:** Generate Pages, Create Components, Theming & Styling, Edit & Refine, Accessibility & Polish, Other / Ask Freely

**PM prompt categories:** Dashboards, Data Tables, Charts & Visualizations, Metric Cards, Recommendations, Starting from Scratch

