## Reusable Helper Components

These are defined at the top of each page file and shared across sections:

### SectionCard
```tsx
function SectionCard({ title, children }) {
  // White card with 32px padding, elevation-100 shadow, 20px bold title
}
```

### CollapsibleSection
```tsx
function CollapsibleSection({ title, children, defaultOpen = false }) {
  // Uses Accordion with a single item. Title is 20px bold in trigger.
}
```

### NumberedList
```tsx
function NumberedList({ items }: { items: string[] }) {
  // Numbered circle badges (brand-subtle bg) + step text
}
```

