## File Checklist for a New Persona Page

- [ ] `GettingStarted[Persona].tsx` — main page with all sections
- [ ] `[Persona]OnboardingQuiz.tsx` — quiz component (separate file)
- [ ] Register both in the router (`client/router.tsx` or equivalent)
- [ ] Add navigation entry to the sidebar layout
- [ ] Add tab to the Getting Started tab group (if applicable)
- [ ] Swap resource links for your project's actual docs/videos/decks
- [ ] Update quiz questions to match the persona's decision points
- [ ] Update prompt generation to reflect the persona's workflow
- [ ] Update reading path to point to your project's actual routes